Interface RdfNodeListener

public interface RdfNodeListener

A listener for RdfNode events, fired by a Model.

Author:
Andreou Dimitris, email: jim.andreou (at) gmail (dot) com
See Also:
Model.addRdfNodeListener(RdfNodeListener)

Method Summary

Method Detail

onTypeChange

void onTypeChange(TypeChange change)
Called when a node changes type.

Parameters:
change - an object representing the occurred type change

onNodeDeletion

void onNodeDeletion(RdfNode node)
Called when a node loses all its triples, which can be thought as deleting that node. Note that this might be called several times for a single node if the node loses all its triples (i.e. deleted), but reused to add some triples back, and loses those triples again.

Parameters:
node - the node that lost all its triples

onNodeAddition

void onNodeAddition(RdfNode node)
Called when a node acquires its first triple, which can be thought as adding that node. Note that this might be called several times for a single node if the node loses all its triples (i.e. deleted), but reused to add some triples back, and loses those triples again.

Parameters:
node - the node that acquired its first triple
